description.en:
1) "My hobbies". Vocabulary: fields of sport, music and other hobbies. Grammar: -ma and -da- infinitive, sufix mine, verb "tegelema", mas-, mast-forms and their usage;
2) "Dream job". Vobabulary: occupations, places of employment, activities. Grammar: translative and essive cases, noun cases: terminative, essive, abessive, comitative, cases in plural; 
3) "This is a great trip". Vocabulary: sightseeing in Estonia and abroad, organizing a trip, buying tickets, finding accommodation. Grammar: locative cases, comparative and superlative, ordinals and cardinals.

